metadata.name: The Ancient One
metadata.description: A celestial sentinel that predates the birth of galaxies, a cosmic sage whispering the ancient hymns of the universe.

metadata.name: Slumbering Spiral
metadata.description: A celestial vagabond spining a cosmic lullaby, inviting all who gaze upon it to partake in the tranquil dance of the universe.

metadata.name: QuasarQuicksilver
metadata.description: The quicksilver marvel that defies the laws of cosmic stillness, carving paths trough the vastness of space.

metadata.name: Eclipsing Vortex
metadata.description: A celestial dreamer in the cosmic symphony, gently weaving tales in the tapestry of the night sky

metadata.name: Dreamweaver
metadata.description: A celestial mistery where cosmic threads interwine and the ethereal dance of reality and dreams converges in the enigmatic grasp of the Dreamweaver Abyss

metadata.name: Uzumaki
metadata.description: Emerging from the convergence of dark energies and otherworldly forces, as if summoned from the nightmares woven by the fabric of the universe. Spiralling away in a dreadful sorrow.

metadata.name: Werther's Lament
metadata.description: A cosmic entity with a heavy heart. Its mournful spin reflects the universal theme of unrequited love, akin to Young Werther's sorrows. Celestial wanderers are drawn by its sorrowful pull, entering a nebular tragedy that mirrors the melancholic tale across the cosmos.

metadata.name: The Jackpot
metadata.description: Gazing into this abyss grants you infinite luck â€“ only if it gazes back.

metadata.name: The Crossroads
metadata.description: At the convergence of celestial pathways, there exists a supermassive black hole of unparalled desolation. Those who chance upon The Crossroads are drawn by an irresistible force â€” a relentess abyss that beckons them into the cosmic crucible.

metadata.name: Abyssal Vacuum
metadata.description: Emerging from the vast reaches of nothingness where not even light can escape, a vast vacuum at the heart of the cosmos.

metadata.name: Umbral
metadata.description: The Umbral casts an eternal nightfall across space, where not even starlight can escape its grasp. The surroundings are held in a cold and longing stillness.

metadata.name: Aquarelle
metadata.description: This cosmic masterpiece is a testament to cosmic artistryâ€”a breathtaking watercolor display that invites observers to marvel at the beauty etched into the canvas of the Universe.

metadata.name: Oculus
metadata.description: The gravitational pull of the Oculus is not just a force of attraction; it is a metaphysical gaze that draws all cosmic matter into the scrutiny of its ever-watchful eyes.

metadata.name: Furor
metadata.description: Furor emanates a fierce and angry glow, a display of intense and vibrant colors that mirror its cosmic wrath.

metadata.name: Morpho
metadata.description: Its playful shapeshifting nature create a mesmerizing display of ever-changing shapes and colors, a cosmic kaleidoscope that defies predictabillity.

metadata.name: Warden
metadata.description: A mysterious and ancient being, the Warden within the blackhole watches over the cosmic expanse with an unwavering and protective gaze. The cosmic whispers within the Oracle echo the wisdom and guidance of the enigmatic Warden, offering cryptic insights to those who approach with reverence.

metadata.name: Vertebrae
metadata.description: Once an incomprehensibly colossal creature of incomprehensible proportions, the ancient colossus defied the limits of the human mind. Its remains, now the vessel of its former greatness, rest in an eternal spiral.

metadata.name: Childhood Void
metadata.description: It is said a child, in the age of discovery, once wandered upon this black hole. The blackhole retained the curiosity of a cosmic child exploring the vastness of space. It now gazes infinitely at the universe with childlike wonder.

metadata.name: Pathway
metadata.description: The Pathway is adorned with celestial trails, guiding cosmic travelers through the vast cosmic expanse.

metadata.name: Guiding Star
metadata.description: The enigmatic Guiding Star, a black hole that serves as a celestial guide for those who venture towards it. Emitting a gentle and guiding light, it stands as a Celestial Beacon, cutting through the darkness to lead all those who wander.

metadata.name: Fateful Embrace
metadata.description: This Oracle is a gateway to the fate of those bold enough to seek it, guiding them through the ebb and flow of their destinies.

metadata.name: Avian Vortex
metadata.description: A black hole adorned with the ethereal presence of cosmic birds in perpetual flight.

metadata.name: Patchwork
metadata.description: A myriad of cosmic fragments, each a remnant of distant galaxies, ancient stars, and celestial phenomena, stitched together to form a beatiful quilted pattern. The Patchwork spans the tapestry of space and time, seamlessly blending the remnants of diverse celestial events into an intricate composition.

metadata.name: Mist Veil
metadata.description: A black hole with a mass that resembles ethereal clouds that drifts and dances within the cosmic winds.

metadata.name: Avalanche
metadata.description: In the heart of a distant galaxy stands a red pyramid... wait, is that a chikn hanging out at the edge of the universe?

metadata.name: Gateway
metadata.description: This black hole is a gateway between realms. A celestial threshold where the fabric of space an time bends to facilitate passage between worlds.

metadata.name: Ripple
metadata.description: The Ripple possesses a mass that undulates with vibrant waves of color, creating a kaleidoscopic spectacle that dances across the cosmic canvas.

metadata.name: Frontier
metadata.description: The Frontier serves as the ephemeral boundary between light and darkness, where cosmic forces converge in a delicate balance of opposing energies.

metadata.name: The Monk
metadata.description: This Oracle carries an enlightened aura, guarded by the serene presence of a cosmic monk, embodying wisdom and tranquility amidst the chaos.

metadata.name: Sanctuary
metadata.description: The Sanctuary is a celestial refuge, where cosmic wanderers find solace and renewal, shielded from the chaotic forces that ripple through the cosmos.

metadata.name: Traverse
metadata.description: The Traverse transcends convential black hole properties, serving as a celestial gateway that allows travelers to travel its depths onto another worlds.

metadata.name: Orb
metadata.description: The Orb acts as a cosmic beacon of attraction, drawing bodies into its gravitational embrace with irresistible force.

metadata.name: The Fall
metadata.description: The Fall represents the eternal descent into oblivion, plunging voyagers into the depths of despair.

metadata.name: Firmament
metadata.description: This black hole embodies the essence of the cosmic firmament, symbolizing the overarching structure and order of the universe.

metadata.name: Lovers
metadata.description: This Oracle symbolizes the eternal bond between cosmic lovers, where their souls interwine in a cosmic array of love and unity.

metadata.name: River Cross
metadata.description: The River Oracle mimics the fluidity of a cosmic river, where celestial currents ripple and flow through the vastness of the universe.

metadata.name: Artist's Dream
metadata.description: By gazing into the abyss, the artist captures the swirling colors and the cosmic brillance of the universe.

metadata.name: Starriest Night
metadata.description: Emerging from the ethereal strokes of an artist's brush, this celestial twilight converges with the cosmic fabric, sculpting the universe into a radiant homage to artistic brilliance.

metadata.name: Reverie
metadata.description: The Reverie Oracle resonates with solitude and introspection. It draws melancholic souls into its depths, offering solace to those lost in contemplative reverie.

metadata.name: Village
metadata.description: For ages, this Oracle has silently watched over the village, witnessing its stories and the passage of time. This black hole stands as a guiding beacon above the quaint village below. For ages, this Oracle has silently watched over the villagers, witnessing their stories and the passage of time.

metadata.name: Maelstrom
metadata.description: Behold the Maelstrom, a starry vortex of unmatched allure and power. This imposing black hole draws all cosmic matter into its swirling embrace.

metadata.name: Volute
metadata.description: The Volute stands as a testament to the ancient forces of the cosmos. This vortex has existed since time-immemorial, a silent witness to the unfolding of galactic epochs.

metadata.name: Whirlwind
metadata.description: The Whirlwind is a paradox among black holes, an enigmatic vortex that not only devours light but also radiates a luminescent aura. With its immense mass, it anchors itself as the central figure in its galactic neighborhood, dictating the motion of all celestial entities around it.

metadata.name: Twister Bride
metadata.description: The Twister Bride is a hauntingly beautiful black hole, named for its legendary absorption of a celestial phenomenon resembling a bride. This black hole boasts a substantial mass, exerting a significant influence on its cosmic surroundings.

metadata.name: Cyclone
metadata.description: The Cyclone is a strikingly vibrant black hole, distinguished by its deep blue hue and intense rotational energy.

metadata.name: Greenlands
metadata.description: You've been high all day. After that nap you took, you woke up in the Greenlands. Try not looking too deep into its void.

metadata.name: Enlightment
metadata.description: The Enlightment Oracle is known among stoners for its mystical ability to elevate consciousness. It has the ability to induce a trance-like state in those who gaze upon it.

metadata.name: Bad Trip
metadata.description: You went too far inside your own mind. Was that last puff really necessary?

metadata.name: Lonely Stoner
metadata.description: The Lonely Stoner gazes upon this Oracle trying to free his mind at night. He looks for peace, but don't seem to attain.

metadata.name: Spliff
metadata.description: The Spliff is a colossal black hole that takes the form of a giant joint, its smoke billowing out into the cosmos and attracting stoners from all corners of the universe

metadata.name: Bonfire
metadata.description: The Bonfire blazes fiercely in the depths of space, a cosmic pyre burning with eternal flames.

metadata.name: Ember
metadata.description: Ember is a fading black hole, once ablaze with cosmic fire but now dwindling into obscurity.

metadata.name: Peak
metadata.description: The Peak rises majestically in the cosmic landscape, resembling a mountain with a perpetual flame burning atop its tip.

metadata.name: Pyromaniac
metadata.description: This black hole is consumed by insatiable pyromania, it burns everything in its path for the sheer pleasure of watching it engulf in flames.

metadata.name: Phoenix
metadata.description: Watch how stronger it rises after it burns.

metadata.name: Xeno
metadata.description: The Xeno black hole emerged from a cataclysmic event where the forces of organic and mechanical energy intertwined, giving birth to a cosmic entity that defies classification. It stands as a testament to the dark beauty of the cosmos.

metadata.name: Reject
metadata.description: The gigerian Reject exists as a grim reminder of the failures and disappointments that litter the cosmic landscape. Its mass, formed by an eternity of discarded dreams, makes for a cosmic landfill that populates the edge of the universe.

metadata.name: Lover's Abyss
metadata.description: The Lover's Abyss portrays the tragic fate of two lovers as they journey into the depths of cosmic despair. Their mass is enmeshed, entwined in a perverse embrace that binds them together for eternity.

metadata.name: Conduit
metadata.description: The Conduit is a black hole whose energy is harnessed and manipulated by a mysterious creature lurking in the depths of space. It is symbiotic, existing in a state of mutual dependence with the enigmatic being that controls its power.

metadata.name: Rift
metadata.description: The Rift is a black hole nestled amidst the desolate remnants of a forgotten city, its presence echoes through the abandoned streets and crumbling structures.

metadata.name: Aurea Chain
metadata.description: The Aurea Chain is a black hole woven from golden chains, an inescapable prison where the condemned and the wayward are drawn, bound for eternity. Its luminous shackles glisten with the weight of cosmic judgment, tightening with each futile struggle. No plea is heard, no escape is grantedâ€”only submission to the unyielding pull of fate.

metadata.name: Emperor
metadata.description: The Emperor dominates the void, a titan among black holes, its event horizon aglow with golden radiance. Neither deceptive nor concealed, it looms with undeniable presence, an emperor of gravity â€” an abyss that does not lure, only demands.

metadata.name: Baroque
metadata.description: The Baroque is a masterpiece of cosmic excess, it does not merely consumeâ€”it curates, selecting only the finest matter and light to vanish within its opulent depths. To gaze upon it is to witness a gravitational symphony, where decadence and destruction are one and the same.

metadata.name: Midas Touch
metadata.description: The Midas Touch is a paradox of cosmic hungerâ€”devouring all, yet leaving nothing behind but gold. Matter, light, even the void itself succumbs to its alchemy, transformed into radiant opulence before vanishing forever.

metadata.name: Golden Weave
metadata.description: The Golden Weave is a black hole of delicate brilliance, its form traced by impossibly thin golden filaments, interwoven like the threads of a celestial tapestry. fragile in appearance yet absolute in force, it ensnares light and matter in an intricate dance before unraveling them into nothingness.

metadata.name: Verdant
metadata.description: In the emerald-deep sectors where no starmap dares extend, Virid Obsidian pulses at the center of a forgotten procession of moons. Its glow is not reflection, but memory: the last breath of dying light trapped in an endless spiral.

metadata.name: Auremald
metadata.description: Its spiral arms stretch like the golden threads of some ancient loom, weaving new laws of motion in defiance of Euclidean reason. Auremerald  doesn't devour, it selects. Those taken are not destroyed, but rewritten.

metadata.name: Cluster
metadata.description: A celestial pantheon collapsed into itself and became one many-eyed god. A sovereign among voids, its silence is composed of many voices. To approach it is to be watched by the absence of sight.

metadata.name: Trivortex
metadata.description: Suspended at the intersection of three galactic currents, Trivortex Axiom balances entropy across planes. Each spiral is a law, each rotation a sentence. Scholars say it doesn't exist in space, but defines it.

metadata.name: Howl
metadata.description: It spins with the fury of a hundred suns unwept. Howl is the echo of a war that ended before time began: a black hole born not of death, but rebellion.

metadata.name: Amarallure
metadata.description: There are black holes that devour stars, and then there is Amarallure, which tempts them. This one's different: elegant, indulgent, almost seductive. It feels like it doesn't consume out of need, but out of desire.

metadata.name: Solari
metadata.description: Solari was first observed transmitting prime numbers into deep space. Then silence. It's unclear whether it was built, born, or merely discovered. But its orbit behaves like a script: one line rewritten. Forever.

metadata.name: Velatrix
metadata.description: This black hole is not a wound, but a blade. Its swirling tendrils carve through galaxies like ritual incisions. No matter dares approach twice.

metadata.name: Monad
metadata.description: A lens? A throne? An engine? The symmetry is too perfect to be natural, too ancient to be artificial. Monad is said to encode the final constant, the number that ends time. Its form is flawless, elliptical, and indifferent. The rings around it are not debris, but encryption.

attributes.value: Collapse of a Prime Reality Thread

metadata.name: Cindervoid
metadata.description: Every empire ends in fire. Cindervoid is the last breath of such an end â€” a spiral forged in apocalyptic heat, still smoking in the language of collapsing suns. Ancient civilizations marked its arrival as an omen. It never left.
